  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: Al-Mudhaffar ibn Muhammad al-Balkhi reported to me. He said: Muhammad ibn Hammam Abu Ali narrated to us. He said: Hamid ibn Ziyad narrated to us. He said: Ibrahim ibn Ubaidullah ibn Hayyan narrated to us. He said: al-Rabee' ibn Sulaiman narrated to us, from Ismail ibn Muslim al-Sakooni, from al-Sadiq Ja'far ibn Muhammad, from his father, from his grandfather, peace be upon them.",
